-- Hermans & Roman Plans to List Stock in Johannesburg
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2012-04-16T05:23:25Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-16/hermans-roman-plans-to-list-stock-in-johannesburg.html
 Hermans & Roman Properties Ltd.,
which manages South African real estate worth about 8.5 billion
rand, said it plans to list its shares on the  Johannesburg Stock
Exchange  during the second quarter.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
